description:
Looking Your Absolute Best has never been Easier or More Convenient!

This Professional Quality Makeup Brush Set gives you all the essential brushes you need to achieve consistently stunning results, right at your fingertips.

All 12 brushes are labeled according to their specific use for your convenient.

Crafted from natural goat hair and the best synthetic bristles for lasting performance, luxurious feel and flawless application, the set includes the 12 must-have brushes professional makeup artists recommend to create and maintain your beautiful look all day long.

This makeup brush set comes in a lovely "Pink" with matching color aluminum ferrule. 

Makeup Brush Holder for Your Convenient

The faux leather carrying case is double as 2 part makeup brush holders for ease of use when you do your makeup.

It will keep all your brushes nice and tidy for everyday use as well as a perfect storage when you are on the go.

Click the Yellow "Add to Cart" Button at the TOP Right of this Page Now to Look Your Absolute Best!
title: Essential Makeup Brush Set - With Makeup Brush Holder - Leather Carrying Case 12 Professional Quality Brushes
